message.body: Could you send me the address in case i dont see you in the norning?
Our finance guys were not able to process the check request today FYI- so I will bring the check home to you on Monday if that's cool.
I have just been assigned to canvass Northfield tomorrow- so I won't be there... bummin!! But my coworker Harper knows to expect you. Thank you so much Gabi!!
